{"id":14288,"date":"2021-08-18T13:57:50","date_gmt":"2021-08-18T13:57:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/?p=14288"},"modified":"2025-04-23T06:15:18","modified_gmt":"2025-04-23T06:15:18","slug":"top-blockchain-app-ideas-for-business-startups","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/top-blockchain-app-ideas-for-business-startups\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 7 Blockchain App Ideas Bolstering the Business Growth"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The global blockchain market is predicted to grow more than a hundred times to<b> 163 billion U.S. dollars<\/b> by <b>2027, <\/b>according to a report by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/1015362\/worldwide-blockchain-technology-market-size\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Statista<\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The growing need for secured mobile applications, simplifying business operations, and smooth supply chain management applications are surging the deployment of blockchain technology in business applications.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain, in simple words, is a technology that offers secured and anonymous transactions. It creates true peer-to-peer secure transactions and has two main jobs-\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Securing the data\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Virtually recording transaction value.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For better understanding, let\u2019s discuss this with an example-\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The internet used to deal with intangibles, like sending or receiving mail or reading and distributing articles. Still, this modern internet works with assets, your valuable items that can be touched and protected. So, these assets are kept in an encoded form on a network-to-network chain i.e. Blockchain.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain has created a buzz since its introduction in 2009; the hype around blockchain has allured many industries to invest in various applications designed in the blockchain. Businesses across the globe are rooting in this ever-evolving technology shift to transform their current business model into more transparent, secure, and reliable. `<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><i>Companies like SAP, IBM, Samsung, and Maersk have already explored a decentralized ledger system via blockchain technology.\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, today, in this blog, I am going to discuss the top 7 blockchain app ideas that will boost your business in 2022-23<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Ok! Then what are we waiting for! Let\u2019s get started!\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<div class=\"cust-secton1 padd-all margin-40\">\n    <div class=\"dis-flex\">\n    <div class=\"colleft\">\n    <div class=\"pb-heading\">Stay Ahead in the Digital Age<\/div>\n    <p>Embrace Blockchain Solutions for Business Expansion.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"colrit\">\n    <div class=\"text-center btn-container\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/contact\" class=\"banner-btn\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_self\">Contact Our Experts<i class=\"cusarrow-icon\"><\/i><\/a><\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<hr \/>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Top_7_Blockchain_App_Ideas_Bolstering_the_Business_Growth_in_2022-23\"><\/span><b>The Top 7 Blockchain App Ideas Bolstering the Business Growth in 2022-23<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Decentralized_Apps\"><\/span><strong>1) Decentralized Apps <\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14896 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-users-growth-1.jpg.webp\" alt=\"DApps_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-users-growth-1.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-users-growth-1.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-users-growth-1.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-users-growth-1.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DApps are digital programs and applications that run on a blockchain or peer-to-peer network of computers instead of a single computer. A DApp stores data in a decentralized database and leverages decentralized computing resources to work. It is one of the trendiest blockchain app ideas in the market.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Based on the blockchain platform, DApps are widely adopted by small and large businesses to trace and track goods as they move across the world and enable cross-border financial transactions without involving any middleman like a clearinghouse or the central bank.<\/span><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-17839 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/blockchain-development.jpg.webp\" alt=\"blockchain development\" width=\"810\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/blockchain-development.jpg.webp 810w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/blockchain-development.jpg-300x56.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/blockchain-development.jpg-768x144.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/02\/blockchain-development.jpg-480x90.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" \/><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><b><i>Chainlink, PokerKing, LBank, and Crypto Kitties <\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">are some of the popular DApps in the market.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bitdegree.org\/crypto-tracker\/top-dapps\/exchanges\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">State of the DApps report<\/a>, the number of active dApps reached 4073, supported by 63k daily active users.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-14297 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-stats.jpg.webp\" alt=\"dapp-stats\" width=\"862\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-stats.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-stats.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-stats.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/dapp-stats.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 862px) 100vw, 862px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_Blockchain_work_in_DApps\"><\/span><b>How does Blockchain work in DApps? <\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Well, DApps are quite tough to build applications and need high expertise thus, you may require to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blockchain-development-company?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=blockchain-14288-d7&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>outsource a blockchain development company<\/strong><\/a> for reliable, secure, and efficient decentralized apps.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><strong>The benefits of blockchain-based DApps are:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Open source code\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">No central point of failure\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Usage of internal currency\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Decentralized consensus mechanism\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr \/>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/a-comprehensive-list-of-blockchain-platforms-to-look-for\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A COMPREHENSIVE LIST OF BLOCKCHAIN PLATFORMS TO LOOK FOR<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Supply_chain_management_app\"><\/span><b>2) Supply chain management app<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14898 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/supply-chain-managment.jpg.webp\" alt=\"supplychainmanagement_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/supply-chain-managment.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/supply-chain-managment.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/supply-chain-managment.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/supply-chain-managment.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The supply chain management app is one of the most adopted blockchain startup ideas that offer real-time analytical systems that efficiently manage the flow of goods and services, including all processes that convert raw materials into final products via the supply chain network.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blockchain-for-supplychain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Blockchain-based supply chain management<\/a> apps will help streamline the workflow and steer processes in the right direction. It includes the active transitivity of a business\u2019s supply chain activities to boost customer value and earn competitive benefits in the marketplace.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b><i>Some supply chain activities include farming, refining, manufacturing, designing, packaging, and transportation<\/i><\/b><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/statistics\/271214\/global-supply-chain-management-software-market-revenue\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">statista.com<\/a>, the global supply chain management software industry generated a revenue of 15.0 billion. The global supply chain management software market revenue from 2008 to 2019.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_Blockchain_work_in_Supply_Chain_Management\"><\/span><b>How does Blockchain work in Supply Chain Management?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14897 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/SCM-managment.jpg.webp\" alt=\"supplychainmanagment_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/SCM-managment.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/SCM-managment.jpg-240x300.webp 240w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/SCM-managment.jpg-768x960.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/SCM-managment.jpg-370x463.webp 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>The benefits of blockchain-based supply chain management apps<\/strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Order management\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Inventory management\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Logistics and shipping details\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analytics &amp;\u00a0 forecasting\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Return management\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Security and scalability\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cloud-based mobility\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Digital_Identity-based_Apps\"><\/span><b>3) Digital Identity-based Apps<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14899 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/digital-Identity-based-apps.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Digital_identity_blockchain-app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/digital-Identity-based-apps.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/digital-Identity-based-apps.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/digital-Identity-based-apps.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/digital-Identity-based-apps.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Digital Identity, in simple words, is information on an entity built on computer systems that represent an external agent. The digital identity app offers a simpler, faster, and safer means for people to prove their identity in different venues, such as websites, businesses, and bars, without producing original documents\u2019 photocopies.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A blockchain digital identity app ensures more secure data storage by offering interoperable, unified, and tamper-proof infrastructure with key advantages to users, enterprises, and IoT management systems.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><b><i>Bluink, Yoti, globaliD\u00a0<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">are some of the digital-identity-based apps in the market.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><i>\u201cAccording to marketsandmarket.com, the global digital identity solutions market has generated a revenue of $13.7 billion in 2019 and it is predicted to reach at $30.5 billion by 2024, at a CAGR of 17.3% from 2019 to 2024\u201d.\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14314 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Untitled-design-26.jpg.webp\" alt=\"digital-identity-solution-market\" width=\"700\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Untitled-design-26.jpg.webp 700w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Untitled-design-26.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Untitled-design-26.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_Blockchain_work_in_Digital_Identity\"><\/span><b>How does Blockchain work in Digital Identity?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14900 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-digital-Identity.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Digital_identity_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"783\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-digital-Identity.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-digital-Identity.jpg-300x294.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-digital-Identity.jpg-768x752.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-digital-Identity.jpg-473x463.webp 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4>The main benefits of blockchain-based digital identity apps<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ease of having duplicate ID proof<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Self-sovereign identity<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Simple and smooth identification\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Non-custodial logic solution\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Decentralized web identity management<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr \/>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Also Read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/how-blockchain-tranformed-fintech\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How Has Blockchain Evolved FinTech For 2024?<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Transportation_Logistics_Apps\"><\/span><b>4) Transportation &amp; Logistics Apps <\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14901 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/transportation-logistics-apps.jpg.webp\" alt=\"transportation_logistics_blockchain_apps\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/transportation-logistics-apps.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/transportation-logistics-apps.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/transportation-logistics-apps.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/transportation-logistics-apps.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain technology in transportation offers immediate, scalable solutions for order tracking, transition, and authentication. With the help of blockchain, the supply chain for truck components and used trucks could be easily tracked on a digital ledger, thus serving as a sort of \u201cCARFAX\u201d on steroids for the commercial transportation market.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Furthermore, blockchain-based <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/industries\/logistics-transportation-software-development?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=blockchain-14288-d7&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">transportation idealist&amp; logistics apps<\/a><\/strong> will be more efficient. A decentralized public ledger system that records all the changes in real-time will help logistic companies to become more efficient through a public ledger system that stores the motions of each shipping container and reduces clerical errors.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Among all technologies, Blockchain technology is witnessed as the most beneficial technology used in transportation &amp; logistics industry apps-\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_blockchain_work_in_Transportation_and_logistics\"><\/span><b>How does blockchain work in Transportation and logistics?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14902 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-transportation-logistics.jpg.webp\" alt=\"transportation_logistics_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-transportation-logistics.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-transportation-logistics.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-transportation-logistics.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-transportation-logistics.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>The main benefits of blockchain-based transportation and logistics apps<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Easy coordination of documents\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduced transportation cost\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Extra care toward sensitive pharmaceuticals\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Easy approval and clearance due to smart contracts\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secured, authenticated, and updated data\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain enables refrigerated containers<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<hr \/>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Also Check: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/top-and-best-companies\/top-blockchain-development-companies\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"bookmark noopener noreferrer\">TOP BLOCKCHAIN DEVELOPMENT COMPANIES<\/a><\/h4>\n<hr \/>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Governments_Voting_Apps\"><\/span><b>5) Governments Voting Apps <\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14903 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/governments-voting-apps.jpg.webp\" alt=\"government_voting_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/governments-voting-apps.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/governments-voting-apps.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/governments-voting-apps.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/governments-voting-apps.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A major issue faced by governments in developing countries is the voting process. Maintaining a high standard of privacy and eliminating tampering with voting could be a cakewalk, but with the help of blockchain-based government, apps can be easily resolved.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A blockchain-based digital government app offers protection of data, streamlined processes, reduced fraud, waste, and better accountability. These apps eliminate a single point of failure and keep the sensitive data of citizens and the government safe.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Parties can exchange information and interact with people on a global and transparent level. <\/span><b><i>According to a McKinsey and Company report of 2013, open data-freely accessible government-sourced data available on the internet can make the world richer by $2.6 trillion.\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_Blockchain_work_in_Government_operations\"><\/span><b>How does Blockchain work in Government operations?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14904 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-Government-operations.jpg.webp\" alt=\"blockchain_works_government_voting_apps\" width=\"800\" height=\"510\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-Government-operations.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-Government-operations.jpg-300x191.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-Government-operations.jpg-768x490.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-works-in-Government-operations.jpg-480x306.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>The benefits of blockchain-based government apps<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reduced redundancy<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Streamline processes<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Increased security and safety\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Decreased audit burden\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better data integrity\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improved efficiency &amp; cost reduction <\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Personal_finance_management_app\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><b style=\"font-family: Dosis, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.2rem; text-transform: uppercase;\">6) Personal finance management app<\/b><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14905 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Personal-finance-management-app.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Personal_finance_management_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Personal-finance-management-app.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Personal-finance-management-app.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Personal-finance-management-app.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/Personal-finance-management-app.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain-based personal finance management app is one of the finest financial <a href=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/40-best-app-startup-ideas\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">blockchain app ideas<\/a> to deploy into the market to add value to the business effortlessly.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nowadays, consumers are more focused on their earnings and savings. Thus, these applications can help businesses gain traction in the market, impelling both startups and investors to look ahead to develop and use a personal finance app.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Further, these applications are working as a significant app in which users can easily categorize their incomes and expenses and track their activity in real-time to get a complete and better understanding of how to manage their finance effectively and smartly.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With blockchain technology, these apps will also offer them an easy connection with all banks and credit card accounts to automatically update the data along with payment reminders.\u00a