ain app idea <\/a><\/strong>for small businesses, start-ups, and enterprises? I guess it is a wonderful idea.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Blockchain technology can positively impact the stock market&#8217;s future in various ways. Currently, many trades pass through a settlement process that takes days due to the involvement of intermediaries, such as clearinghouses, exchanges, and regulatory processes.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But in the case of blockchain networks, settlement times get dropped to minutes from days and offer improved and reduced error transactions. This stock market blockchain app idea facilitates trading in a new digital asset.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_does_the_Blockchain_work_in_the_stock_market\"><\/span><b>How does the Blockchain work in the stock market?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14908 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-work-in-the-stock-market.jpg.webp\" alt=\"stock_market_blockchain_app_ideas\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-work-in-the-stock-market.jpg.webp 800w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-work-in-the-stock-market.jpg-300x150.webp 300w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-work-in-the-stock-market.jpg-768x384.webp 768w, https:\/\/www.invertio.in\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/blockchain-work-in-the-stock-market.jpg-480x240.webp 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The benefits of blockchain in the stock market are<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better interoperability &amp; trust\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-w